{"tid":1964003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[MSMD]新加坡新增142起病例 140起為本地感染","createTime":"2020-04-08T13:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T14:25:10.000Z","uid":253608,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5490cff403023cdb0443a15c83fa70d492c63d8c","tid":1964003,"uid":253608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T13:26:37.000Z","msg":"source: <a href=\"https://www.8world.com/news/singapore/article/covid-142-new-cases-1095616\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.8world.com%2Fnews%2Fsingapore%2Farticle%2Fcovid-142-new-cases-1095616&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbt8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=dc561578\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.8world.com/news/singapore/article/covid-142-new-cases-1095616</a><br />\n我國今天（8日）新增142起確診病例，其中140起為本地感染病例，創下單日最高紀錄。我國至今總病例累計達到1623起。<br />\n<br />\n衛生部在文告中說，新增的病例中只有兩起是輸入型病例，其餘的140起都是在本地感染的。<br />\n<br />\n本地病例中的55起跟已知的感染群有關，13起跟之前的確診病例有關，剩下的72起暫時與之前病例無關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://assets.mediacorp.sg/image/upload/s--wcxlPBt4--/c_scale%2Cw_780/f_auto%2Cq_auto/8April142cases.jpg?itok=zbcmIFi-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.mediacorp.sg%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fs--wcxlPBt4--%2Fc_scale%252Cw_780%2Ff_auto%252Cq_auto%2F8April142cases.jpg%3Fitok%3DzbcmIFi-&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbt8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=1bccb7ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://assets.mediacorp.sg/image/upload/s--wcxlPBt4--/c_scale%2Cw_780/f_auto%2Cq_auto/8April142cases.jpg?itok=zbcmIFi-</a>"},{"pid":"be060fb6f45c6572528d4cc95b7e117548cd6909","tid":1964003,"uid":189109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T13:38:35.000Z","msg":"monkey see monkey do<br />\nmonkey do monkey sick<br />\nmonkey sick monkey die"},{"pid":"22026edea82fe0ac03a9634cc84b3bc174eccb23","tid":1964003,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T13:38:43.000Z","msg":"坡仔呢單好奇怪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名32歲印度籍男子今天（8日）在家中病逝，之後才確診感染了2019冠狀病毒，當局正在調查他的死因。<br />\n<br />